*.xmpdata
# ...but thesis_CIM_v6.xmpdata is a SOURCE file, not a build artifact: it carries
# the PDF/A metadata + CC BY-NC-ND license (title, author, rights) that pdfx reads
# at build time. Keep it tracked so a fresh clone can reproduce the PDF/A.
!thesis_CIM_v6.xmpdata

# Generated outputs (regenerated by pipeline)
README.html
REPRODUCIBILITY.html
output/
tasks/

# outputs/ : *.rds intermediates already covered by the *.rds rule above.
# Ignore redundant/superseded renders; keep the hero-figure PDF (embedded in the
# thesis) and the small precomputed-fallback CSVs.
outputs/hero_figure_2x16_ranking.png
outputs/istanbul_ranking_preview.pdf
outputs/istanbul_ranking_preview.png

